{"tid":466883,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"24歲，無晨勃，扯唔起…","createTime":"2017-11-13T03:43:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T02:58:26.000Z","uid":29540,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"d069fd584906f9bf517a9a9a6489640857e1e60f","tid":466883,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T03:43:13.000Z","msg":"求救，各位ching細佬我24歲 常做運動 做gym 不煙不酒 正常生活1年前左右已經有扯旗唔夠硬的情況但無理佢 直至近依3個月，晨勃突然消失 同女友做愛時 勃起有困難 硬唔夠十秒即軟 勃起條j唔夠90度 條j勃起後既硬度軟到連套都帶唔到 覺得自己好無用 這種心情比死更難受睇過西醫 條友一口咬定話我唔夠訓 睇過中醫 就話我腸胃濕 同開左少少補腎藥材比我 2個都無料到 自己走去萬x 買d海狗丸 瑪卡丸食又係無料到 究竟咩事&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"9681d3303aa95cf890a526f4c81682a47f633692","tid":466883,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T03:44:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e25ff3243fe9af3e8ff90049be31391e2c042aa1","tid":466883,"uid":45148,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T03:47:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://ent.qingdaonews.com/images/attachement/jpg/site1/20131230/e89a8f2aabce142afef82e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.qingdaonews.com%2Fimages%2Fattachement%2Fjpg%2Fsite1%2F20131230%2Fe89a8f2aabce142afef82e.jpg&h=e778e31b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7c1c8cbd7755fb79a4a54e9b8228c1dc9005bc3f","tid":466883,"uid":14250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T03:48:53.000Z","msg":"偉哥應該幫到你"},{"pid":"a67c46fa1187809b0e325257661ddd2da20ed060","tid":466883,"uid":1977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T03:48:59.000Z","msg":"試下男人"},{"pid":"890f204340d7bb54f6faad8b35030cfb036a6b97","tid":466883,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":27,"score":-25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T03:50:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20160427/photo/bkn-20160427214504903-0427_00862_001_09p.jpg?20160428025226\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20160427%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-201